                  <rs id="t18570615-679-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18570615-679-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18570615-679-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="burglary"></interp>, Burglariously breaking and entering the dwelling house of <persName id="t18570615-name-66" type="victimName">
