                  </hi>. (<hi rend="italic">Policeman, F</hi> 117). I produce a certificate—(<hi rend="italic">Read: "Guildhall Sessions, Thomas Reid, Convicted April</hi>, 1855, <hi rend="italic">of housebreaking and larceny; 
Confined eighteen months</hi>")—I was present—the prisoner is the person—I was not engaged in the case, but he was confined at our station before his trial, and I had an opportunity of seeing him there.</p>
